text: Kamilla Mammadova (born 31 August 1996) is an Azerbaijani women's football defender. Currently, she plays for Ugur FC and is a member of the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:Adana İdmanyurduspor players Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriate sportspeople in Turkey Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Turkey
